18
00:02:00,324 --> 00:02:02,664
You can tell Father Geoghan
it won't be much longer.

19
00:02:03,994 --> 00:02:07,224
Now Sheila, you know
what a good work...

20
00:02:07,254 --> 00:02:09,504
the Church does in
the community...

21
