Father out of the parish...

23
00:02:14,714 --> 00:02:17,114
and this will never happen again.

24
00:02:18,694 --> 00:02:20,874
We'll just be another moment Paul.

25
00:02:21,484 --> 00:02:22,484
Of course Father.

26
00:02:23,544 --> 00:02:26,644
Now Sheila, I'm going to
give you my personal card.

27
00:03:04,214 --> 00:03:06,114
Losing a good reporter...

28
00:03:06,514 --> 00:03:07,554
is always tough.

29
00:03:08,474 --> 00:03:10,534
But losing one of our best...

30
00:03:10,994 --> 00:03:13,674
