35
00:03:22,624 --> 00:03:25,324
Oh, well, thanks Ben. I think.

36
00:03:26,254 --> 00:03:27,584
Although I take issue...

37
00:03:27,904 --> 00:03:30,744
with your reference
to my seniority.

38
00:03:30,914 --> 00:03:33,894
I will say that Stewart's
departure is specially...

39
00:03:33,914 --> 00:03:36,174
painful for me, because...

40
