I can't ever eat at those things,
they are kinda depressing.

62
00:04:35,504 --> 00:04:36,504
I know.

63
00:04:37,264 --> 00:04:38,564
Did you see the numbers
from Washington?

64
00:04:38,565 --> 00:04:39,765
Yeah, very interesting.

65
