Hey, that's great.

237
00:11:48,814 --> 00:11:51,754
We covered Geoghan when the
story broke 3 years ago.

238
00:11:51,784 --> 00:11:53,104
Baron was still in Miami.

239
00:11:53,124 --> 00:11:55,263
I think he was at the
Times then actually.

240
00:11:55,264 --> 00:11:56,264
He wasn't here.

241
00:11:56,294 --> 00:11:58,304
So do you think that
sue has a chance?

242
00:11:59,264 --> 00:12:02,884
